        "subject": "LU-2641 ldiskfs: handle missing ext4_ext_cache->ec_type",
        "message": "LU-2641 ldiskfs: handle missing ext4_ext_cache->ec_type\n\nCommit b05e6ae5 (v2.6.37) dropped the ec_type member from struct\next4_ext_cache because it can be generated using a combination of\nthe ec_len and ec_start values.\n\nWe introduce a helper to do the same when the member isn't present.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jeff Mahoney <jeffm@suse.com>\nChange-Id: I8f69ce65fd2b05fa712a298ed91f85930177edb5\n"
